        {
            "title": "聯儲會副主席傑斐遜稱面對不確定因素 利率處於良好位置",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Alessandro Rampazzo/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E8g3L2rwnKZ_iGFK2_2dyw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f1f6e069135cd63a6621f7d03665a307\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Alessandro Rampazzo/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會副主席菲利普·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"傑斐遜\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:傑斐遜;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/傑斐遜\">傑斐遜</a>表示，伊朗戰爭將在短期內加劇<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"不確定性\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:不確定性;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/不確定性\">不確定性</a>，並推高美國通膨，但央行的政策設置仍然是適當的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">傑斐遜表示，目前的利率大致處於既不會刺激經濟、也不會抑制經濟的區間。他稱當前的立場將支持就業，並隨著關稅影響的減弱，使通膨率回落到2%的目標水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">傑斐遜周二在為底特律梅西大學一場演講準備的講稿中說：「我對前景仍持謹慎態度。經濟形勢的不確定性很高，能源價格上漲和中東衝突加劇了這種不確定性。但我仍然認為，我們目前的政策立場是恰當的，能夠讓我們評估經濟的走向。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cd223795-4509-3621-ad5f-ae15eb46f32e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"聯儲會副主席菲利普·傑斐遜攝影：AlessandroRampazzo/彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8wK.Zo4i..gKrNRGsx_9Iw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1f219f5da80d892a8eb49419ee68acd8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲會副主席菲利普·傑斐遜攝影：AlessandroRampazzo/彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">傑斐遜表示，他預計通膨下降的整體趨勢將會持續，但他對伊朗戰爭對通膨和消費者需求的影響持謹慎態度，稱這場衝突使他對物價的預期變得複雜。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">傑斐遜說：「然而，近期能源價格上漲至少在短期內會對整體通膨構成上行壓力。持續的貿易政策不確定性和地緣政治緊張局勢也給我的通膨預測帶來上行風險。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">傑斐遜還對勞動力市場表達了謹慎態度，他形容勞動力市場大致處於平衡狀態，但容易受到最近這輪不確定性的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">傑斐遜說：「如果目前高度不確定的局面持續下去，企業可能會持續不願招聘，從而在更長時間內抑制就業成長。在評估勞動力市場潛在脆弱性的同時，我將繼續密切關注未來的就業成長速度。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Jefferson Says Rates Well Positioned Amid Uncertainty</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E5%82%91%E6%96%90%E9%81%9C%E7%A8%B1%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%8D%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0-%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E8%99%95%E6%96%BC%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE-222708060.html",
